                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
                    <i class="fas fa-info-circle text-primary-500 mr-2"></i>
                    At <strong>Friberg Car Rentals</strong>, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information.
                    This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our services.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Table of Contents -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center">
                <i class="fas fa-list text-primary-500 mr-3"></i>
                Table of Contents
            </h2>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li><a href="#section1" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium">1. Information We Collect</a></li>
                <li><a href="#section2" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium">2. How We Use Your Information</a></li>
                <li><a href="#section3" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium">3. Information Sharing and Disclosure</a></li>
                <li><a href="#section4" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium">4. Data Security</a></li>
                <li><a href="#section5" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium">5. Your Rights</a></li>
                <li><a href="#section6" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium">6. Cookies and Tracking</a></li>
                <li><a href="#section7" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium">7. Third-Party Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="#section8" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium">8. Changes to This Policy</a></li>
                <li><a href="#section9" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium">9. Contact Us</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 1 -->
        <div id="section1" class="mb-12 scroll-mt-24">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-database text-primary-600 text-xl"></i>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">1. Information We Collect</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="pl-16 space-y-4 text-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6">Personal Information</h3>
                <p>When you register or book a rental, we collect:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Full name and contact information (email, phone number, address)</li>
                    <li>Date of birth and driver's license details</li>
                    <li>Payment information (credit/debit card details)</li>
                    <li>Booking history and preferences</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6">Automatically Collected Information</h3>
                <p>We automatically collect certain information when you visit our website:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>IP address and browser type</li>
                    <li>Device information and operating system</li>
